metadata.name: AND WHEN THE NIGHT COMES #1
metadata.description:
Montevideo, Uruguay 2019
Photography by Aaron Sosa
www.aaronsosaphotography.com

6000 X 4000 px 300dpi  / JPG

Aaron Sosa is a photographer and visual artist currently living in Montevideo, Uruguay, where he works for agencies, international editorials and corporate clients. His work has been exhibited in over 110 galleries worldwide.
